com.adobe.fd.signatures.pki.client.types.common

Enum HashAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<HashAlgorithm>
      • com.adobe.fd.signatures.pki.client.types.common.HashAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<HashAlgorithm>

    public enum HashAlgorithm
extends Enum<HashAlgorithm>
    Represents hash algorithms used to digest the PDF document. You create an instance of this type when you sign or certify a PDF document.
